oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kentucky Fried Chicken Logo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Kentucky Fried Chicken (Firm); Logos (Symbols);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white image of the Kentucky Fried Chicken logo, featuring a Kentucky Fried Chicken restaurant, an image of Colonel Sanders, and the tagline "We Do Chicken Right." On the back of the image, a typed note says, "KFC Logo 5/82" and a handwritten note says "73 pica's wide words and Col. Sanders only."
